Nicholas C. Fanandakis





Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer, E. I. du Pont de Nemours and Company
An ITT director since October 2016, Mr. Fanandakis brings to the board significant financial and operational expertise and deep insight in the industrial market space having served as Chief Financial Officer and in a number of other financial and executive management positions during his extensive tenure with E. I. du Pont de Nemours and Company.
 







